text: Jil Walton (born July 5, 1966) is an American equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:American female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the United States Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Arcadia, California
